      <scopecontent id="aspace_de4b8d3e1092ca9d7e547db02e4669d9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, statements, endowment and gift files, and memoranda documenting financial transactions of the Yale University Library Business Office.</p>  
